---
// Global footer with company info and navigation
---
<footer class="bg-black text-gray-400 py-16">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-10 mb-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-1">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-5">
          <img src="/logo.png" alt="Praeternum" class="w-8 h-8 object-contain" />
          <span class="font-display text-lg font-medium text-white">Praeternum</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed">ネットワーク工事を、もっとシンプルに。</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white text-sm font-medium mb-5">サイトナビ</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-xs">
          <li><a href="/#service" class="hover:text-white transition">サービス内容</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#flow" class="hover:text-white transition">導入の流れ</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#coverage" class="hover:text-white transition">対応エリア</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#faq" class="hover:text-white transition">よくある質問</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#contact" class="hover:text-white transition">お問い合わせ</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white text-sm font-medium mb-5">運営情報</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-xs">
          <li>Praeternum</li>
          <li>創業：2026年</li>
          <li>所在地：兵庫県三木市吉川町みなぎ台2-35-1</li>
          <li>Email：contact@praeternum.com</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white text-sm font-medium mb-5">その他</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-xs">
          <li><a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-white transition">プライバシーポリシー</a></li>
          <li><a href="/terms" class="hover:text-white transition">利用規約</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pt-8 border-t border-gray-900 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-3 text-xs">
      <span>© 2026 Praeternum. All rights reserved.</span>
      <span class="text-gray-600"></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
